OL,3,CRegional Covid-19 restrictions 'did
OL,4,Cnot change behaviour' during 2020 `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FRegional restrictions did not change
OL,8,Fpeople's behaviour during the
OL,9,Fcoronavirus pandemic despite rising
OL,10,Fnumbers in Scotland, a study indicates.
OL,12,FResearchers from the University of
OL,13,FAberdeen examined adherence to
OL,14,Frestrictions including social
OL,15,Fdistancing, mask-wearing, staying at
OL,16,Fhome and handwashing, and found people
OL,17,Fin high or low restriction areas
OL,18,Fbehaved no differently to each other.
