OL,3,CRegional Covid-19 restrictions 'did
OL,4,Cnot change behaviour' during 2020 `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FThe study, published in the US journal
OL,8,FTranslational Behavioral Medicine,
OL,9,Flooked at behaviour during the Covid-
OL,10,F19 pandemic in Scotland from March to
OL,11,FNovember 2020, with 1724 people
OL,12,Finterviewed at random to get a
OL,13,Frepresentative sample.
OL,15,FPeople did not alter behaviour to
OL,16,Ffollow enhanced local restrictions
OL,17,Fduring the pandemic, the study found,
OL,18,Fand the restrictions may have been
OL,19,Fmore effective if based around factors
OL,20,Fother than just coronavirus cases
OL,21,Faccording to new research.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
