OL,3,CRegional Covid-19 restrictions 'did
OL,4,Cnot change behaviour' during 2020 `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FThe study compared people's behaviours
OL,8,Fbefore and after local restrictions,
OL,9,Fand compared behaviours of those
OL,10,Fliving in areas with increased
OL,11,Frestrictions to those living in areas
OL,12,Fwithout.
OL,14,FPeople did not change their behaviour
OL,15,Fwhen restrictions were tightened,
OL,16,Fincluding social distancing and mask
OL,17,Fwearing, defying scientists'
OL,18,Fexpectations, research showed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
