OL,3,CRegional Covid-19 restrictions 'did
OL,4,Cnot change behaviour' during 2020 `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FIt also found people in high or low
OL,8,Frestriction areas behaved no
OL,9,Fdifferently to each other, and
OL,10,Fexamined "intention and self-efficacy".
OL,12,FIntention and self-efficacy related to
OL,13,Fkeeping a 2.0 metre distance was
OL,14,Fassessed by asking: "Do you intend to
OL,15,Ffollow all the government
OL,16,Finstructions..." and "How confident or
OL,17,Fnot are you that you can follow the
OL,18,Fgovernment instructions..." graded on
OL,19,Fa scale, according to the report.
