OL,3,CRegional Covid-19 restrictions 'did
OL,4,Cnot change behaviour' during 2020 `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FThe respondents answered questions
OL,8,Fabout their behaviours from the past
OL,9,Fweek, including if they had left home,
OL,10,Fhad adhered to the social distancing
OL,11,Frule, worn a mask in a shop or on
OL,12,Fpublic transport and if they washed
OL,13,Ftheir hands as soon as they got home.
OL,15,FDr Chantal den Daas, senior lecturer
OL,16,Fin health psychology, in collaboration
OL,17,Fwith the Covid Health and Adherence
OL,18,FResearch in Scotland (Charis) project,
OL,19,Fsaid the research "can effectively
OL,20,Finfluence public behaviour" in the
OL,21,Ffuture.
