OL,3,CRegional Covid-19 restrictions 'did
OL,4,Cnot change behaviour' during 2020 `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,FShe said: "When local restrictions
OL,8,Fwere introduced in 2020 due to an
OL,9,Fincrease in Covid-19 case numbers, we
OL,10,Fthought we would see a change in
OL,11,Fbehaviour after they were implemented.
OL,12,FBut this was not what we found.
OL,14,F"It is really important to build an
OL,15,Funderstanding of what could have been
OL,16,Fdone differently and how we can
OL,17,Feffectively influence public behaviour
OL,18,Fin the future should we be faced with
OL,19,Fanother public health crisis.
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@AOU
