OL,3,CRegional Covid-19 restrictions 'did
OL,4,Cnot change behaviour' during 2020 `
OL,5,Cstudy
OL,7,F"This research provided insight on the
OL,8,Ftype of information we should aim to
OL,9,Fcollect in future pandemics, to see if
OL,10,Fwe can find better measures to predict
OL,11,Fcases, examine the need for
OL,12,Frestrictions and the effect of any
OL,13,Frestrictions put in place.
OL,15,F"Future research in acute outbreaks
OL,16,Fshould assess behaviour and beliefs
OL,17,Fabout the virus, risk on an ongoing
OL,18,Fbasis and identify the need for
OL,19,Fintervention even before cases rates
OL,20,Fstart to go up."
